Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.29,0:00:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是… 那陔子真正的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.48,0:00:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎吧！直到銀河的盡頭!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧… 阿爾特…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:31.36,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 敵主炮發射!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能再由你們任意擺佈了\N{\fs10}\N{\r}蘭花也是，Vajra也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross Quarter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.05,0:01:05.48,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 太慢了啊，奧茨瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.61,0:01:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 抱歉，有點事耽擱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.39,0:01:13.39,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 奧茨瑪少校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 笨蛋，要叫隊長，Skull-3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull-3… 隊長!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了\N{\fs10}\N{\r}為了打破Galaxy的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及在背後的格蕾斯·奧康納\N{\fs10}\N{\r}和她的同夥的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:34.29,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你說Galaxy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的，我們被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.29,0:01:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被他們的陰謀和他們的支持者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼根據說那樣的胡話!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證據的話，證據的話我有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:50.42,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Skull-4的IFF
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我… 看到了\N{\fs10}\N{\r}那傢伙的原形
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是蘭花\N{\fs10}\N{\r}攻擊那個假象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:11.82,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.76,0:02:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:31.53,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- Battle Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不是應該被Vajra幹掉了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三島總統閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍後請您詳細解釋\N{\fs10}\N{\r}也包括格拉斯總統的暗殺事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:45.35,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(197,420)}- 暗殺?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(373,420)}總統不是被Vajra殺死的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}- 怎麼可能，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧，雷昂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:55.38,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 被識破了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 意外地很能幹呢，那些少年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:03:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6464FF&}沒關係\N{\fs10}\N{\r}也只有現在能讓他們做場美夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，Battle Galaxy中的大量熱源\N{\fs10}\N{\r}發射出來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:13.06,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 這是… Ghost V9！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你說V9?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:32.30,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- Skull-3呼叫Skull-4，阿爾特前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 聽到的話就快回話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡，柯嵐上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:41.02,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 來，接住了，阿爾特，你的機體！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull-4呼叫Battle Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說，雪露\N{\fs10}\N{\r}這次一定把蘭花救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，把你的力量借給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用你的歌把那傢伙喚醒吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:59.80,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 歌?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:03:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是啊，你的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了哦，大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候，聽到了你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的… 內心的呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.33,Default italize,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會思考的是鮮花\N{\fs10}\N{\r}會思考的成不了鮮花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要，跟隨著感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要，飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全機，上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:01.43,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 「突擊 Love Heart!」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米歇爾，給我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙，尤哈妮，佩特洛\N{\fs10}\N{\r}現在就解除你們的枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去，曾讓Macross City\N{\fs10}\N{\r}陷入恐怖深淵的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,JUDAH系統，釋放！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭花，聽到了嗎?\N{\fs10}\N{\r}我的聲音，雪露的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.33,Default italize,,0000,0000,0000,,醒過來吧，蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌聲，取回你真正的歌聲吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.74,Default italize,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，連接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:17.12,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 強烈的Fold波，史無前例的級別
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:32.50,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- Fold Wave，急速展開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 星系全域正在構造網絡結構！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:38.63,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 隊長，Vajra的行動…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Galaxy混蛋，到底幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，感覺到了… 感覺到了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FE00&}這是星座，這是銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Little Queen什麼的，已經沒用了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(269,460)}我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(375,460)\c&H6464FF&}得到了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了，蟲子們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在已經將全宇宙掌握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連Protoculture都對這力量\N{\fs10}\N{\r}感到害怕，嚮往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用Vajra的力量\N{\fs10}\N{\r}最終神化成為這種姿態的超時空生命體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:19.27,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 這聲音… 格蕾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 這麼巨大…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:31.85,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不起作用?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 這是… 次元斷層
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對直接和Quee連接的我們來說\N{\fs10}\N{\r}歌已經毫無意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，膜拜吧!\N{\fs10}\N{\r}與支配命運的神等同的我們的力量!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼，我的耳，我的手足\N{\fs10}\N{\r}與那強韌的利爪一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6464FF&}好好記住，我們的力量吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，蘭花，阿爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經… 不行了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好，蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中彈的緣故，總算逃脫了他們的支配
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，歌唱吧，蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷，憤怒，喜悅\N{\fs10}\N{\r}把你所有的心情，融入歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，這次一定要阻止這場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們兄妹的救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這歌聲是… 蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌聲將Vajra…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於蘭花·李的歌聲\N{\fs10}\N{\r}Vajra的攻擊停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:17.88,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什麼，不是背叛到敵方去了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，在與Vajra女王的Fold波相抗衡\N{\fs10}\N{\r}範圍不斷擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起來，雪露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣，我的工作已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有留下，什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請回想起來，雪露小姐\N{\fs10}\N{\r}因為有雪露小姐在，我才能起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為有雪露小姐的力量\N{\fs10}\N{\r}阿爾特才能飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:09.58,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,420)}雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6464FF&\pos(350,419)}阿爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,460)}你說過吧，決不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，所以來吧，雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是，你們是… 我的雙翼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，再一次飛翔吧，雪露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向此戰場上的所有士兵通告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra並不是我們真正的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy和篡奪Vajra女王的格蕾斯·奧康納\N{\fs10}\N{\r}才是我們真正的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以羽翼為驕傲的人啊\N{\fs10}\N{\r}與我們一同前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲波坐標確認
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pin-Point Barrier集中在主炮前端
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，無謂的掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:34.20,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 朝向Island 1的直擊過來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什麼！?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被Vajra… 保護了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:09.53,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳達到了嗎\N{\fs10}\N{\r}歌聲，我和雪露小姐的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra也有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，和我們很不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼人類全都分散著各自\N{\fs10}\N{\r}做著不同的事，它們無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以Vajra想從難以理解的人類裡\N{\fs10}\N{\r}把可以用Fold波溝通的我救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，在感覺到和我不同的\N{\fs10}\N{\r}雪露小姐的歌聲後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解到我們每個人都是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不把心意好好傳達的話\N{\fs10}\N{\r}就無法彼此理解的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它們終於明白了這點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:15:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家，相互擁抱吧\N{\fs10}\N{\r}直到銀河的盡頭!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王的協議無法傳輸?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是歌的力量嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斷層護盾再次展開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣才能突破呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通道… Vajra在斷層中打開了通道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全軍，跟著Vajra前進!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主炮損傷，無法射擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在，Macross Attack！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧，阿爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:18.63,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們的未來！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們的希望！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾特，這個交給你了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米歇爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不明白嗎?\N{\fs10}\N{\r}這才是人類進化的終極姿態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼進化啊\N{\fs10}\N{\r}明明只是讓Vajra犧牲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:59.63,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我來掩護你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(288,460)}- 佈雷拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(371,460)\c&HFFFFFF&}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:03.67,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 阿爾特，瞄準女王的腦袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 腦袋?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra的心不在腦袋上，而是在肚子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra是在肚子中歌唱的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些臭蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你們接觸後，終於理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:24.72,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不論走到哪裡，人都是單獨的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6464FF&}- 所以我們要…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FE00&\pos(242,460)}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(361,460)}正是因為一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才會愛上某個人啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:55.26,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 這就是Vajra的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:21:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶，如果說Vajra是\N{\fs10}\N{\r}不需要交流的物種的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這歌… 曾作為什麼的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:07.59,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「求愛之歌」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:13.55,Default italize,,0000,0000,0000,,求愛?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra在數萬年中\N{\fs10}\N{\r}不，數億年一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與別的銀河中所居住的群族相遇\N{\fs10}\N{\r}為了求偶而歌唱的求愛之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AIMO AIMO\N{\fs10}\N{\r}就是 「親愛的  親愛的」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.38,0:22:13.15,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 阿爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.38,0:22:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6464FF&}- 阿爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.53,0:22:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪露與蘭花所帶來的\N{\fs10}\N{\r}真正的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.37,0:22:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋正在飛翔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.48,0:22:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個，雪露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.21,0:23:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會輸的\N{\fs10}\N{\r}歌也好，戀愛也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受你的挑戰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.34,0:23:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在，才開始呢
